      "content": "see, that's exactly what i'm thinking. the second option sounds way more likely. it's like they aren't trying to keep me quiet, they're trying to keep me close. i've noticed that since the move, they've been giving me 'special projects' that involve oversight on the exact departments i was questioning. it's like they're literally putting me in a cage made of gold to see if i'll fold. what do you think their end goal is with that kind of setup?",
